# Production: keep the API base empty so the app calls relative "/api/..." paths that are
# proxied (by Nitro routeRules / vercel.json) to the backend on the SAME origin. This makes
# the auth cookies first-party (vercel.app), instead of blocked third-party onrender.com cookies.
#
# IMPORTANT: If you set VITE_API_BASE_URL in the Vercel dashboard, it OVERRIDES this file.
# Remove/empty that dashboard variable so production uses the proxy.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
